---
const title = "Cranbalt - Tower Cranes & Steel Structures";
---

<html lang="lt">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>{title}</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Cranbalt - Tower crane rental, manufacturing of industrial cranes and steel structures in Baltics & Nordic countries." />
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body { font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }

    /* Navigation */
    nav {
      background: rgba(0, 48, 135, 0.95);
      color: white;
      padding: 1rem 5%;
      position: fixed;
      width: 100%;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 1000;
    }
    .nav-container {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .logo { font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: bold; }
    .nav-links a {
      color: white;
      margin-left: 2rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    /* Hero */
    .hero {
      background: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.65), rgba(0,0,0,0.65)), 
                  url('https://cranbalt.com/wp-content/uploads/your-hero-image.jpg') center/cover no-repeat;
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 220px 20px 160px;
      margin-top: 70px;
    }
    .hero h1 { font-size: 3.2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .hero p { font-size: 1.35rem; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto 2rem; }

    .container { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 60px 20px; }
    h2 { color: #003087; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- Navigation -->
  <nav>
    <div class="nav-container">
      <div class="logo">Cranbalt</div>
      <div class="nav-links">
        <a href="#">Tower Cranes</a>
        <a href="#">Manufacturing</a>
        <a href="#">Projects</a>
        <a href="#">About Us</a>
        <a href="#">Contact</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="hero">
    <h1>Half a century of lifting solutions</h1>
    <p>The highest quality tower cranes rental, manufacturing of industrial cranes and steel constructions.</p>
    <a href="#services" style="background:#003087; color:white; padding:16px 40px; text-decoration:none; border-radius:6px; font-size:1.1rem;">Find Out More</a>
  </section>

  <!-- Services -->
  <div class="container" id="services">
    <h2>Tower crane rent</h2>
    <p>Cranbalt offers a wide range of tower cranes (8t to 40t) in Baltic and Nordic countries.</p>

    <h2>Manufacturing</h2>
    <p>We manufacture bridge cranes, gantry cranes, steel structures, cantilever racks and other heavy equipment.</p>

    <h2>Who we are</h2>
    <p>With roots dating back to 1966, Cranbalt combines long experience with modern technology to deliver the best lifting solutions in the region.</p>
  </div>

</body>
</html>
